{"tid":683469,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"魔迷紋身「歌頌」卡利奧斯","createTime":"2018-05-29T17:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T07:44:24.000Z","uid":119157,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1e8bb97e55f280c8d4ba5ca83e1ff7370787b6","tid":683469,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=oJS3i7CeAujLbCyY0SqyweargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=36b6f130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】抽水無極限，有曼聯球迷為了「紀念」卡利奧斯出錯而令利物浦失落歐聯，竟然把這名門將的名字紋在身上。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯及利物浦是世仇，當紅軍在上周六歐聯決賽以1:3不敵皇家馬德里失落冠軍之後，一眾紅魔球迷開心得像愛隊奪冠一樣。門將卡利奧斯（Loris Karius）兩度犯錯導致失球，頓時成為魔迷的英雄。<br />\n<br />\n有一名魔迷更把卡利奧斯的「功績」紋在身上，紋了「卡利奧斯是一名傳奇2018年5月26日」在手上。這個紋身的相片其後在網上流傳，如此挑釁，當然引來不少利迷留言反擊，有人說：「當魔迷因為利物浦落敗才能慶祝，真是令人傷感。」<br />\n<br />\n至於卡利奧斯本人周一跟隨利物浦大軍從基輔飛回英國，數小時後就坐飛機離開；看他在機場的表情仍然是悶悶不樂，相信十分需要度假去放鬆心情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=21596151136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D21596151136&d=oJS3i7CeAujLbCyY0SqyweargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=7d9ce1e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=21596151136</a><br />\n<br />\n曼迷朋友啲思路真係好難令人理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c73e068df0e7b158157b722fb4a2bf99d1b9626","tid":683469,"uid":37747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"椰子都有銅像，冇理由唔整個多卡列奧斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce764c96e97abaf8bdb4a9dd65d1e567a93f466","tid":683469,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c73e068df0e7b158157b722fb4a2bf99d1b9626","tid":683469,"uid":37747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"椰子都有銅像，冇理由唔整個多卡列奧斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29